{"tid":997872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【僱主喜訊】英國連鎖超市Tesco將裁員1.5萬人 自動販賣機取代員工食堂","createTime":"2019-01-27T13:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T02:32:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"8bdc6215bba3093be0d06d40a48317071247ccac","tid":997872,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190127/large/1548569346_700a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190127%2Flarge%2F1548569346_700a.jpg&h=d8fd1b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190127/59191111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190127%2F59191111&d=VkPAZ4LKujINdWeCQe5UZU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=bda7aaa7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190127%2F59191111&h=b5f99044\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190127/59191111</a><br />\n<br />\n外電報道，英國連鎖超市集團Tesco將削減約1.5萬個職位，並關閉肉類、魚類和熟食櫃檯。<br />\n<br />\n據〈星期日郵報〉報導，Tesco還將對店內麵包店進行重修，並用自動販賣機取代員工食堂，料計劃影響集團旗下較大型的732家店舖。<br />\n<br />\n行政總裁Dave Lewis本週較早期時候將通知有關員工，並且被迫進行裁員談判。報道引述，Tesco回覆〈星期日郵報〉指，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公司一直尋找更簡單有效的運營業務方法。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5547b6bc8052238bea5055fdc33fd82ca05d5b4e","tid":997872,"uid":179967,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:31:18.000Z","msg":"香港依家一半一半咁做 等人熟哂點用再普及D就可以連34.5都省埋"},{"pid":"c18e5693f2b87847175caf2e679125daa040b160","tid":997872,"uid":79563,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"5547b6bc8052238bea5055fdc33fd82ca05d5b4e","tid":997872,"uid":179967,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:31:18.000Z","msg":"香港依家一半一半咁做 等人熟哂點用再普及D就可以連34.5都省埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n長遠減低成本, 一定要係自動化及電腦化<br />\n<br />\n日本東京係世界上最多自動售賣機密度既地方"},{"pid":"e81b225519c1d7157807995c54db960840eec400","tid":997872,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:36:15.000Z","msg":"並用自動販賣機取代員工食堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6e8734c4578cfaa761b33f014d98ca0e79006e","tid":997872,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:37:15.000Z","msg":"琴日去一田排曬長龍 d自助機無人用<br />\n去圓方果間超級市場又係無人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2517e599d2b0b015f18f2601087a65832008e0a","tid":997872,"uid":123774,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"ac6e8734c4578cfaa761b33f014d98ca0e79006e","tid":997872,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:37:15.000Z","msg":"琴日去一田排曬長龍 d自助機無人用<br />\n去圓方果間超級市場又係無人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:39:37.000Z","msg":"只係習慣問題<br />\n電子野你唔俾人選擇佢地就會用<br />\n你睇大陸老人家到街市到街邊乞衣都識用wehcat pay就知"},{"pid":"80b9d3be2cb13b8036123abe93c3eb599fc315d2","tid":997872,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e81b225519c1d7157807995c54db960840eec400","tid":997872,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:36:15.000Z","msg":"並用自動販賣機取代員工食堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:42:12.000Z","msg":"新鮮野變雪藏野"},{"pid":"8893f80c8666db28691838e0597d0e7ca337a0f7","tid":997872,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ac6e8734c4578cfaa761b33f014d98ca0e79006e","tid":997872,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:37:1